{"word":"Standard","slug":"standard","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Standard</b> An ensign used by each of the tribes of Israel in camp and march<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=52'>Num 1:52</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=2'>Num 2:2</a><br/> Banners used as<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=20&verse=5'>Psa 20:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=6&verse=4'>Son 6:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=6&verse=10'>Son 6:10</a><br/> Used in war<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=4&verse=21'>Jer 4:21</a><br/> Used to direct the route to defensed cities<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=4&verse=6'>Jer 4:6</a><br/> Used to call attention to news<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=2'>Jer 50:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=12'>Jer 51:12</a><br/><a href='S:Armies'>Armies</a>; <a href='S:Banner'>Banner</a>; <a href='S:Ensign'>Ensign</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=49&verse=22'>Isa 49:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=62&verse=10'>Isa 62:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=4&verse=6'>Jer 4:6</a>"}]}